<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:500,700&amp;subset=cyrillic" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  h1, p {
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
<title>{{ title }}</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: 'verdana', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 25px; color: #000; background-color: #e5e5e5; overflow: auto; padding: 0 16px;">
<div style="min-width: 375px; max-width: 900px; width: 100%; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 0;">
  <div style="display: table; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 30px;">
    <div style="display: table-cell; width: 50%; vertical-align: middle;">
      <a href="{{ store_url }}" title="{{ store_name }}">
        <img src="{{ logo }}" alt="{{ store_name }}" style="border: none; height: 63px;" />
      </a>
    </div>
    <div style="display: table-cell; width: 50%; vertical-align: middle; text-align: right; line-height: 22px;">
      <p>{{ store_phone }}<br>{{ store_email }}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="background-color: #fff; padding: 30px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 30px; line-height: 37px;">Спасибо!</h1>
      <p style="margin: 0;">мы свяжемся с вами для уточнения заказа</p>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top: 60px;">
      <div style="display: table; font-weight: bold; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 48px;">
        <div style="display: table-cell; width: 50%; vertical-align: middle;">
          Заказ №{{ order_id }}
        </div>
        <div style="display: table-cell; width: 50%; vertical-align: middle; text-align: right;">
          {{ date_added }}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display: table; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 60px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 2em;">
        <div style="display: table-row;">
          <div style="display: table-cell; width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;">
            Имя и фамилия: {{ payment_address_fields.firstname }}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="display: table-row;">
          <div style="display: table-cell; width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;">
            E-mail: {{ email }}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="display: table-row;">
          <div style="display: table-cell; width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;">
            Телефон: {{ telephone }}
          </div>
        </div>
        {% if payment_address_fields.company %}
        <div style="display: table-row;">
          <div style="display: table-cell; width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;">
            ИНН компании: {{ payment_address_fields.company }}
          </div>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        <div style="display: table-row;">
          <div style="display: table-cell; width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;">
            Адрес: {{ payment_address_fields.address_1 }}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="display: table-row;">
          <div style="display: table-cell; width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;">
            {{ order_comment }}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display: table; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 40px; line-height: 1.5em;">
        <div style="display: table-header-group;">
          <strong style="font-size: 16px; padding: 8px 0; display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; white-space: nowrap;">{{ text_product }}</strong>
          <strong style="font-size: 16px; padding: 8px 6px; display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; white-space: nowrap;">Кол-во</strong>
          <strong style="font-size: 16px; padding: 8px 6px; display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; white-space: nowrap;">{{ text_price }}</strong>
          <strong style="font-size: 16px; padding: 8px 0; display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; white-space: nowrap; text-align: right;">{{ text_total }}</strong>
        </div>
        {% for product in products %}
        <div style="display: table-row;">
          <p style="font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0; display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle;">{{ product.name }} {% for option in product.option %}<br /><small>{{ option.name }}: {{ option.value }}</small>{% endfor %}</p>
          <p style="font-size: 14px; padding: 0 6px; display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle;">{{ product.quantity }}</p>
          <p style="font-size: 14px; padding: 0 6px; display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; white-space: nowrap;">{% if product.price_old > product.price %}<span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38); text-decoration: line-through; white-space: nowrap;">{{ product.price_old }}</span><br>{% endif %}{{ product.price }}</p>
          <p style="font-size: 14px; padding: 8px 0; display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; text-align: right; white-space: nowrap;">{{ product.total }}</p>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <div style="display: table; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 2em;">
        {% for total in totals %}
        <div style="display: table-row;">
          <p style="display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle;">{{ total.title }}</p>
          <p style="display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; text-align: right; white-space: nowrap;">{{ total.text }}</p>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; color: #888;">
    <p>Вы получили это письмо, потому что оформили заказ на сайте {{ store_url }}</p>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>